dat1 %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Treatment, y = BMD))+
  geom_boxplot()+
  geom_point()

plotmeans(BMD~Treatment, data = dat1)

dat1 %>% 
  ggplot(aes(sample = BMD))+
  geom_qq()+
  geom_qq_line()

bmd_model <- aov(BMD~Treatment, data = dat1)

plot(bmd_model, which = 1:2)
